 of that monad, where F_T is
defined by (x\xrightarrow {f} y)\mapsto  (x\xrightarrow {f} y\xrightarrow {\eta _y} Ty) and 
U_T is
defined by (x\overset {f}{\rightsquigarrow } y)\mapsto  (Tx\xrightarrow {Tf} T^2y\xrightarrow {\mu _y} Ty).

